        <choice_table/>
        <column_label>Requester Name</column_label>
        <comments>Mandatory String(100) capturing the external requester's name. Populated by the case_submit scripted REST endpoint from the portal submission page. NOT exposed by case_status_lookup per AAP Section 0.7.4. Use synthetic names only per AAP Section 0.7.2 (No-PII constraint). Replaces ArkCase CaseFile.getOriginator()'s PersonAssociation lookup with a flat String column for the POC.</comments>
